Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.38,0:00:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I found a number in my account.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.69,0:00:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Fifty-seven dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.57,0:00:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It was already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.21,0:00:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I hadn't lost a single trade yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.64,0:00:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I can't code.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.12,0:00:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}9 years in crypto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.18,0:00:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}AI trades my thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.92,0:00:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}For 15 days I'd been watching win rate and outcomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.90,0:00:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}62 trades, 48 percent — within what I thought was fixable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.40,0:00:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Then that afternoon I added another column — fees 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Funding 27.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.38,0:00:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Combined, 57 dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.35,0:00:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}My real trading losses were only 14.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.65,0:00:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Which means: even if I made zero mistakes, the account would still be bleeding — because holding a position costs rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.32,0:00:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'd stared at that 14 dollars for 15 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.01,0:00:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The 57 that actually put me in the red was the column I hadn't looked at.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.32,0:00:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If you optimize the wrong column, more effort makes it worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.68,0:01:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 17 tomorrow — I shipped a rule I don't trust myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.81,0:01:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Follow along.
